{"id":"elishua","term":"Elishua","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>God his salvation, a son of David, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 5:15\">2 Sam. 5:15</a> = Elishama, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 3:6\">1 Chr. 3:6</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 5:15","1 Chronicles 3:6"]}